\chapter*{Abstract}
\addcontentsline{toc}{chapter}{Abstract}

Mental health has become a major concern in today’s fast-paced world, where individuals frequently experience stress, anxiety, and emotional imbalance due to academic pressure, work stress, and personal challenges. Access to proper mental health support is often limited because of factors such as high cost, lack of awareness, social stigma, and limited availability of professionals.

To address these challenges, HealMate is developed as a web-based mental health support system that provides simple, accessible, and effective solutions for improving mental well-being. The system focuses on helping users maintain emotional balance through daily wellness activities, simple remedies, and self-care practices that can be easily followed in everyday life.

HealMate includes features such as daily tasks, mood tracking, health insights, and expert guidance, enabling users to manage their mental health effectively. The platform is accessible anytime and anywhere through smartphones or computers, making it convenient and user-friendly.

The system is developed using modern web technologies such as HTML, CSS, and JavaScript for the frontend, and Supabase for backend services including authentication, database management, and real-time communication.

Overall, HealMate aims to make mental health care simple, affordable, and accessible while promoting self-awareness, stress management, and positive thinking, helping individuals lead a healthier and more balanced life.

